snippet.title: Street Race Kings - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Today I will be announcing 'Project 5' as 'Street Race Kings'! For those that have been following, Project 5 has been the project name for a while when providing updates on progress, and now the game is far enough to give it a name! Very excited with this title, will be focusing on an open world racing game, in which you can race and explore in various maps, various event types, customize vehicles and more! Will keep you posted on progress!

PlayStation Wishlist: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10010835
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2909100/Street_Race_Kings/
